{"tid":1995231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新官上任 民政局新局長用特大電腦MON上FB(冇登入)","createTime":"2020-04-30T05:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T15:26:29.000Z","uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d7445f5142c14569da714c5057f3a5df9bd686","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"民政事務局呼籲市民避免前往長洲參與太平清醮活動（附圖）<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/29/P2020042900421.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F29%2FP2020042900421.htm&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=56c8baea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202004/29/P2020042900421.htm</a><br />\n民政事務局局長徐英偉（左）和副局長陳積志（右）今日（四月二十九日）透過網上平台，了解二○二○年（庚子年）長洲太平清醮活動的情況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202004/29/P2020042900421_photo_1172195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F29%2FP2020042900421_photo_1172195.jpg&h=8e3fd5c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db93134808fcab9dd648afcecfe52545a8fe08bf","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"行政長官唔可以係政黨成員，點解「政治委任官員」就可以？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1984185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1984185</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民政事務局局長 徐英偉</span><br />\n財經事務及庫務局局長 許正宇<br />\n商務及經濟發展局副局長 陳百里<br />\n政務司司長政治助理 蕭嘉怡<br />\n<br />\n自由黨<br />\n財經事務及庫務局副局長 陳浩濂<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長政治助理 符傳富<br />\n<br />\n<del>(已退民主黨)<br />\n勞工及福利局局長 羅致光(IQ160)</del>"},{"pid":"d717f290a86fabc2abc34c9100b57ac9a4757614","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"周圍打卡 忙到<br />\n<br />\n到訪灣仔民政諮詢中心<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202004/27/P2020042700236_photo_1172163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F27%2FP2020042700236_photo_1172163.jpg&h=cfc1cda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到訪香港中央圖書館及銅鑼灣運動場<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202004/28/P2020042800327_photo_1172192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F28%2FP2020042800327_photo_1172192.jpg&h=296fbd72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與香港工會聯合會物業管理業屬會會面<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202004/22/P2020042200823_photo_1172147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202004%2F22%2FP2020042200823_photo_1172147.jpg&h=5fdf37de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdc7d19f3b75ddceb638ba25f5ac95fb3c3dcbf7","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"民政事務局涉及的範疇極多，包括康樂體育、文化、博彩、公民教育、青年政策、地區行政等等。<span style=\"color: red;\">其中地區行政，亦即和區議會合作，是最容易涉及政治爭議的層面。</span>該局需要聯繫地區組織網絡、和區議員打交道、掌握民情。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民政事務局掌握「地區水喉」，能調撥政府資源。現時17區區議會由民主派主導，與政府關係緊張。相信徐英偉其中一項最重要工作，就是在合法的情況下，弱化民主派區議會的角色</span>，壯大建制派地區組織的聲勢，幫助立法會選舉的選情。"},{"pid":"ce0cd1cc5593b80090e799aef09615662cfedaba","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"下設部門及公營機構<br />\n民政事務總署（<span style=\"color: red;\">民政事務處（專員）</span> - 牌照事務處）<br />\n政府新聞處<br />\n康樂及文化事務署（古物古蹟辦事處 -文物修復辦事處）<br />\n物業管理業監管局<br />\n香港消費者委員會"},{"pid":"a745c779f141fdda3570b39a313a241023f6738e","tid":1995231,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"偉哥有啲料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ddfb0a382bd7d7b787a3535d9cc5b4603a25fd","tid":1995231,"uid":327593,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"屌好撚似大陸文宣"},{"pid":"418ae214a2b91009f21ba0125f99160e0cb44e01","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6ddfb0a382bd7d7b787a3535d9cc5b4603a25fd","tid":1995231,"uid":327593,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"屌好撚似大陸文宣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e27aede2fb95b94af31b5fee6660dcf7d882da0","tid":1995231,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151cb641ffea22599236e2ecd393f772bf2996f0","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a745c779f141fdda3570b39a313a241023f6738e","tid":1995231,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"偉哥有啲料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"搵佢幫你啃咗啲公仔"},{"pid":"a23302c0306dc7d11aef2e4401ede601665d8df2","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e27aede2fb95b94af31b5fee6660dcf7d882da0","tid":1995231,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:54:33.000Z","msg":"民政事務局今日表示，自3月起，民政局已完成發放資助予九個主要演藝團體、14個康樂及文化事務署的場地夥伴藝團、33個獲民政局藝能發展資助計劃資助的團體、香港藝術節協會和海事博物館，涉款超過5,000萬元，用以支付員工、承辦人員和自由工作者的薪金。<br />\n<br />\n海事博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />董建華野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132683d76371e934fbb