30T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚近睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n使唔使3D眼鏡"},{"pid":"7a4fed3701bb55428519493fd11a856b58ec6bfe","tid":1995231,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"幾時搞c drive上網大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7a4645b2e7e647c10344be06ebce3fe87227c5","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"當局同區議會嘅關係好緊張，再加上之前民政事務總署削減區議會撥款，已惹起好大嘅反彈，徐英偉上任局長只有個幾禮拜，亦未見有聲氣約見18區區議會正、副主席，依家又要面對兩項社區重點項目計劃或入稟法庭提出司法覆核，可謂「櫈都未坐暖」就遇着難題啦！唔知佢點拆彈？<br />\n民政事務總署回覆我哋，話音樂噴泉當時得到大部分區議員支持，亦喺2018年11月30日獲財委會撥款，有關嘅建築工程合約完全符合法律同程序要求嘅招標過程而簽訂。而音樂噴泉項目嘅工程現正進行中，預計於下年年中完成，又話如果工程日後進入法律程序，將按照一貫程序處理喎。"},{"pid":"86281f749e4e8a47ac2fef5ecf64921b5bf4ee2a","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a4fed3701bb55428519493fd11a856b58ec6bfe","tid":1995231,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"幾時搞c drive上網大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c1/Pot_core2.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20081210034209\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc1%2FPot_core2.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20081210034209&h=3eaa34e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vbPlSDE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvbPlSDE.gif&h=5942041c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ea5bad1f0be87912211df9f50784cc295ac5196","tid":1995231,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"今年太平清醮好似佢未上任之前都話咗取消啦喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fbf560bee30354f2a6649af67872e2ad64327b","tid":1995231,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"有博電上到網，好先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025aadb2d344aca7b9c7caadca4cd058dcafe639","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea5bad1f0be87912211df9f50784cc295ac5196","tid":1995231,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"今年太平清醮好似佢未上任之前都話咗取消啦喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:26:29.000Z","msg":"新渡輪表示，截至下午五時，已接載約19000人次來往中環及長洲，較去年同期減少約42%。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"bdc7d19f3b75ddceb638ba25f5ac95fb3c3dcbf7","tid":1995231,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"民政事務局涉及的範疇極多，包括康樂體育、文化、博彩、公民教育、青年政策、地區行政等等。<span style=\"color: red;\">其中地區行政，亦即和區議會合作，是最容易涉及政治爭議的層面。</span>該局需要聯繫地區組織網絡、和區議員打交道、掌握民情。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民政事務局掌握「地區水喉」，能調撥政府資源。現時17區區議會由民主派主導，與政府關係緊張。相信徐英偉其中一項最重要工作，就是在合法的情況下，弱化民主派區議會的角色</span>，壯大建制派地區組織的聲勢，幫助立法會選舉的選情。"}}